	   <tr><td colspan=2>Any SKs out there have any thoughts on Combat Stabiity / Innate Defense vs. Combat Agility / Lightning Reflexes?<br><br>This seems to be a hotly contested issue and wanted to get some additional thoughts, if possible.&nbsp;&nbsp;=)<br><br>Luna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
